    Docket Analytics and Reports RSS Files Last Week in Dockets

RSS Files

Source: vignettes/RSS.Rmd
RSS.Rmd

This page is updated Monday through Friday, hourly between 9AM ET and 5 PM ET. It presents RSS files for the various dockets tracked by the nrcadams package. The last update was at 2023-05-25 10:18:17.647514 ET.

These RSS files are still under testing and development. Use at your own risk.

Making RSS files

The following code shows the user how they can generate RSS files to help keep updated with their favorite ADAMS search results.

last_week_in_dockets = nrcadams::docket_codex |>
  dplyr::pull(DocketNumber) |>
  nrcadams::search_docket(days_back = 7) |>
  dplyr::left_join(nrcadams::docket_codex) |>
  dplyr::filter(!is.na(Project))
#> Searching with the following URL:
#>  https://adams.nrc.gov/wba/services/search/advanced/nrc?q=(mode:sections,sections:(filters:(public-library:!t),properties_search_any:!(!(DocketNumber,eq,'99902088',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'05000610',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'05000608',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'99902071',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'07007027',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'99902111',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'99902100',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'99902094',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'99902079',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'99902076',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'99900003',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'99902049',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'05200048',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'99902078',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'05200050',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'99902069',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'05007513',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'99902095',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'99902101',''),!(DocketNumber,eq,'05200049','')),properties_search_all:!(!(PublishDatePARS,gt,'05/18/2023',''))))&qn=New&tab=advanced-search-pars&z=0 
#> : 2.487 sec elapsed
#> 
#>  This search returned: 267 files.
#> Joining with `by = join_by(DocketNumber)`

here::here("docs", "RSS") |> dir.create(recursive = TRUE)

nrcadams::docket_codex |>
  dplyr::pull(Project) |>
  purrr::walk(\(.x) {
    last_week_in_dockets |>
      dplyr::filter(Project == .x) |>
      nrcadams::write_rss(
        file = here::here("docs", "RSS", paste0(
          .x |> stringr::str_replace_all(" ", "_"), ".rss")
          ),
        title = .x 
        )
  })

Locations of Locally Supported RSS Files

The RSS files generated on this page and updated by this site are located at the URLs shown in the table below.

nrcadams::docket_codex |>
  dplyr::select(Project) |>
  dplyr::mutate(`RSS File` = paste0(
    "https://mrdenman-nuclear.github.io/nrcadams/RSS/",
    Project |> stringr::str_replace_all(" ", "_"),
    ".rss"
  )) |>
  dplyr::add_row(
    Project = "All Dockets", 
    `RSS File` = "https://mrdenman-nuclear.github.io/nrcadams/RSS/dockets.rss"
    ) |>
  nrcadams::hyperlink_file_to_name(name_vct = `RSS File`, url_vct = `RSS File`)|>
  DT::datatable(escape = FALSE)
